  "body": "In this PR https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2295/files we introduced an index to efficiently check which attestations have the same data root.\r\n\r\nHowever checking Lighthouse Aggregation Pool https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/stable/beacon_node/beacon_chain/src/naive_aggregation_pool.rs we could just pre-aggregate attestations and keep a single attestation per data root.\r\n\r\nThis would substitute the need for the index in the first place and reduce the amount of data we have to keep around.",
